Done! I've created a complete Space Invaders game at `/workspace/space-invaders.html`. 

**Features included:**
- **Canvas rendering** with retro green/neon styling
- **Keyboard controls**: Arrow keys to move, Space to shoot, P to pause, R to restart
- **Scoring system**: Points vary by enemy type (10, 20, 30 points)
- **Lives system**: Start with 3 lives, lose one per enemy hit
- **Wave progression**: Difficulty increases with each wave (enemies faster, more numerous)
- **Collision detection**: Player bullets vs enemies, enemy fire vs player
- **Game mechanics**:
  - Enemies move side-to-side and down
  - Enemy AI with random shooting
  - Wave clear detection with bonus points
  - Game over on 0 lives or enemies reaching bottom
- **UI**: Real-time score, lives, and wave display
- **Visual polish**: Retro neon green aesthetic with shadows and glows

Just open the file in a browser to play!
